# Common Prompts

## Inspect This Repo And Summarize Architecture
Inspect this repository and summarize the architecture, major modules, build/test entry points, data flows, and areas that look high risk for change.

## Implement This Task Using Task Brief
Read `docs/ai/task-brief-template.md` or the completed task brief, inspect the relevant files first, then implement the task with small isolated changes, preserving public contracts unless the brief says otherwise.

## Review This Diff
Review this diff for correctness, maintainability, security, performance, test coverage, contract compatibility, and documentation gaps. Prioritize concrete findings.

## Generate PR Description
Generate a pull request description that summarizes the problem, the approach, notable tradeoffs, validation performed, and any follow-up work.

## Identify Missing Tests
Inspect the changed files and identify missing unit, integration, or regression tests. Be specific about scenarios and assertions.

## Update AGENTS.md Based On Feedback
Update `AGENTS.md` based on the latest repo conventions, tooling, and team feedback. Keep it concise, practical, and specific to this repository.
